divs: Sighting DetailsSitting around the camp fire there were 4 of us that saw this thing that looked like a star(no flashing lights as on a plane), it moved across the sky for about a min. than ziped off at what seemed like 10,000 mph in a blink of an eye, sorry I dont have a photo all I know is what we saw.
